source.name: IDES - Claimants for regular (non-Federal) unemployment insurance benefits, Legislative Districts
source.description: The Dashboard contains information on Illinois claimants for regular (non-Federal) unemployment insurance benefits. The reports are organized by legislative district and feature claimant information by education, age, and military status. Explanations of definitions and methodology are included in the technical notes.
